@page "/packages"

<PageTitle>Packages</PageTitle>

<section class="page-panel">
    <h1>Package dependencies</h1>
    <p>This template references <code>MachSoft.Template.Core</code> from NuGet and expects the package to be available in the configured internal feed.</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Update <code>NuGet.config</code> with your corporate feed URL.</li>
        <li>Restore the application with <code>dotnet restore</code>.</li>
        <li>Keep the shared baseline version aligned with the template package guidance.</li>
    </ul>
</section>
